# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   Comment on the line below if you are fine with check-in it.
#.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different platforms, they may not be able to install the same dependencies.
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock can be gitignored or not, depending on your needs.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock can be gitignored or not, depending on your needs.
# pdm.lock

